{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/About.png?t=1737191161\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/AssistantSummon.gif?t=1737191161\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SUMMON ASSISTANTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Summon all sort of weird whimsical <strong>creatures</strong>. From a clueless monkey to a cute pile of goo. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/Ingredient.gif?t=1737191161\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COOK INGREDIENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make one weird soup by combining different <strong>magic ingredients</strong> together! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a unique mechanic of chain reactions, Cauldron Caution offers lots of depth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/Deck.gif?t=1737191161\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD YOUR DECK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build a <strong>custom deck</strong> of your<strong> favorite creatures and ingredients</strong> from your ever-growing <strong>collection</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/RichNarrative.gif?t=1737191161\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FOLLOW A RICH NARRATIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shyla the Shyder is a <strong>strange pink insect lady</strong> that only seems to fall from one predator to the next. Until one day, she finds the opportunity to <strong>fight back</strong> by summoning other <strong>creatures</strong> to her side and cooking dubious <strong>magic recipes</strong> with her trusty <strong>cauldron</strong> !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cauldron Caution has a lot of charming NPCs to interact with, along with lots of bad jokes and crazy situations. A very energetic adventure awaits! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/PvP.gif?t=1737191161\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ONLINE PvP MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenge</strong> your friends and strangers online to intense <strong>duels</strong>!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737191161","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737191161","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737191161","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737191161","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3023740,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/About.png?t=1737191161\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991890/extras/AssistantSummon.gif?t=1737191161\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SUMMON ASSISTANTS</h2><